{"tid":1506520,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢入機場前應該有既準備","createTime":"2019-08-25T23:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T01:06:52.000Z","uid":161115,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2a423b64c9ea7a11760656884bcc8195896188d2","tid":1506520,"uid":161115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T23:24:35.000Z","msg":"之前發夢入機場時唔太完美，有好多旅客不滿行程受阻，但可以改善<br />\n<br />\n其實應該係發夢時入機場前同旅客預告定？<br />\n<br />\n例如發夢時係某年某月某日開始入機場，甚至係諗住做長時間癱瘓。咁應該係個日早最少一星期係不同介別例如網上同世界各地預告定等佢地有所預備？<br />\n<br />\n如果咁做至少唔會比人屌，有足夠時間通知<br />\n<br />\n但係正式多人入個日之前唔建議親身入機場宣傳，始終個度有張禁人入既魔法陣，人太少有咩損害就唔好<br />\n<br />\n利申發夢<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論點先可以更完美"},{"pid":"0d264a6390b9dea7e84ed2b127f480dd8d4faaa2","tid":1506520,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:01:49.000Z","msg":"真係一起身無哂啲機場post架喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506546</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b21990167537d8009db1830572ddd33c25a987a7","tid":1506520,"uid":161115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd1b31b68df5d5308be7c95bc3d8b3195ab70948","tid":1506520,"uid":210612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uoFrpMD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuoFrpMD.png&h=623f3a78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cf9efbfc31f2575846ba01560a0ac717cc0efa6","tid":1506520,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KVKR1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F